If there is, and she remembers my name, could you please have her reply to me?[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
The moment my eyes scanned the lines, a small "Ah" escaped my parted lips.[r]
[_tb_end_text]

