The ringing tone repeated several times, each time nudging my heart further and further to the edge of its seat.[l][r]
Please pick up... Please pick up...[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
And then, my prayer was answered.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

