"Chito? Is it really you?!"[r]
I was so overwhelmed that I nearly shouted, letting out a quiet cough afterward.[r]
"Yeah, it's me. I'm... I'm so glad... Ishii, you also came to this world..."[l][r]
She was undoubtedly referring to our modern society as "this world." Her voice trembled, brittle-sounding words escaping her so shakily that it became apparent; she was on the verge of tears.[l][r]
"Yes, it's me.," I sternly spoke into the phone, as if I was trying to reinstate my own existence.[r]
"I'm so glad. I never thought the day would come when I could speak to you again... I didn't think it was possible."[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

