"... M-Me too. Me too."[r]
Chito whispered weakly, an audible sniff hitting my ears.[l][r]
"Are you okay? Are you doing well?! What happened after... everything?!"[r]
I barraged the girl with questions, my voice quickly rising in intensity. My heart was pounding in my ears; how could I calm myself down right now?![r]
I knew that I shouldn't rush, that I shouldn't be so brash, but the words just kept flying out of my mouth.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"Yeah... yes... I'm f-fine, just... wait. J-Just..."[r]
Chito interrupted me, her voice so unsteady it was almost as if she'd burst into tears at any moment.[l][r]
"Oh... sorry. Right, let's take it easy," I said, trying to calm us both down.[r]
"Yeah..."[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

