... This is bad. Chito might be having a panic attack.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
But without knowing where she is, there's nothing I can do besides talking to her on the phone.[l][r]
Damn it... Asking about Yuuri off the bat was too careless...![l][r]
What should I do? Tell her to hang up and call for an ambulance? Or ask if there's anybody nearby to help?[l][r]
Either way, if Chito faints or breaks down, there’s nothing I can do.[r]
What should I do?... What <i>can I do?!</i> And just then, in the midst of my scramble...[l][r]
[cm]Chito gasped, her heavy breaths getting through the phone. "... Haa... Haah... I'm okay... I just got a little surprised..."[r]
Chito's weakened voice rang into my ear.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
