"Are you alright?" I ask.[r]
"Yes... I'm okay n-now..."[l][r]
I took notice of her irregular breathing and hoarse, gravelly voice. She didn’t sound okay at all.[r]
I forgot that Chito was probably at school and that I was at work... I just stood there, hoping that she would calm down.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

